{"title":"数据结构-基础树结构","uid":"bc36d13ad9232edecc9b42fb7ab0884b","slug":"笔记/算法和数据结构/数据结构/基础树结构","date":"2024-05-24T12:00:03.000Z","updated":"2025-10-30T16:36:51.519Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/笔记/算法和数据结构/数据结构/基础树结构.json","keywords":null,"cover":"img/post/笔记/算法和数据结构/数据结构/基础树结构/cover.jpg","content":"<p><a href=\"%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%2F%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%2F%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA\">&lt;返回算法与数据结构导航</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h1 id=\"一-树的-adt-和定义\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#一-树的-adt-和定义\"></a> 一. 树的 ADT 和定义</h1>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>In computer science, a tree is an abstract model of a hierarchical structure. A tree consists of nodes with a parent-child relation.<br />\n在计算机科学中，树是层次结构的抽象模型。树由具有父子关系的节点组成。</p></blockquote>\n<p>树是由n（n&gt;0）个有限节点组成一个具有层次关系的集合。</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-树的特点\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-树的特点\"></a> 1. 树的特点</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>每个节点都只有有限个子节点或无子节点</li>\n<li>没有父节点的节点称为根节点</li>\n<li>每一个非根节点有且只有一个父节点</li>\n<li>除了根节点外，每个子节点可以分为多个不相交的子树</li>\n<li>树里面没有环路(cycle)</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"2-树的术语\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-树的术语\"></a> 2. 树的术语</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>术语</th>\n<th>种类和名称</th>\n<th>介绍</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>树的节点</td>\n<td><code>Node node</code></td>\n<td>树的基本单位。树是由多个节点的组成的<br>每个节点包含元素、父节点和子节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>父节点</td>\n<td><code>Node parent</code></td>\n<td>若一个节点含有子节点，则这个节点称为其子节点的父节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>子节点</td>\n<td><code>Node[] children</code></td>\n<td>一个节点含有的子树的根节点称为该节点的子节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>兄弟节点</td>\n<td><code>Node[]</code></td>\n<td>具有相同父节点的节点互称为兄弟节点；</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>节点的度</td>\n<td><code>degree: Node → int</code></td>\n<td>该节点的子树总个数<br>也可以说子节点的总个数</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>树的度</td>\n<td><code>degree: Tree → int</code></td>\n<td>最大的节点度称为树的度</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>根节点</td>\n<td><code>Node root</code></td>\n<td>树中不具有父节点的节点<br>一棵树只有一个根节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>叶节点</td>\n<td><code>Node leaf</code><br><code>Node external</code></td>\n<td>不具有子节点的节点<br>也可以说度为<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span> 的节点<br>一棵树可以由多个叶节点<br>二叉树的叶节点可以为空节点 <code>null</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>内节点</td>\n<td><code>Node internal</code></td>\n<td>具有至少一个子节点的节点<br>也可以说度不为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span> 的节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>祖先节点</td>\n<td><code>ancestors: Node → Node[]</code></td>\n<td>递归定义：<br>1. 该节点的父节点 <br>2. 该节点的父节点的祖先节点<br>这些节点的集合是该节点的祖先节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>祖孙节点</td>\n<td><code>descendant: Node → Node[]</code></td>\n<td>递归定义：<br>1. 该节点的子节点 <br>2. 该节点的子节点的祖孙节点<br>这些节点的集合是该节点的祖孙节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>节点的深度</td>\n<td><code>depth: Node → int</code></td>\n<td>该节点的祖先节点的个数<br>根节点的深度为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>节点的高度</td>\n<td><code>height: Node → int</code></td>\n<td>该节点到达树叶的最长路径长度<br>叶节点的高度为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>树的高度</td>\n<td><code>height: Tree → int</code></td>\n<td>最大的叶节点深度<br>或者说从根节点到叶节点最长的路径(不包括根节点)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"3-树的种类\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#3-树的种类\"></a> 3. 树的种类</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">种类名</th>\n<th>介绍</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">有序/无序</td>\n<td>无序树/自由树：树中任意节点的子节点之间没有顺序关系<br>有序树/搜索树/查找树：树中任意节点的子节点之间有顺序关系</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">平衡/不平衡</td>\n<td>绝对平衡树: 任意节点的子树之间两两高度差绝对值不超过 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span><br>平衡树: 所有叶节点在同一层<br>不平衡树：所有叶节点不一定在同一层</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">分叉情况</td>\n<td>1. 等差树：每个内节点的子节点个数都相同<br>2. 不等叉树：每个节点的键值个数不一定相同、子节点个数也不一定相同</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"4-树的-adt-组成成分\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#4-树的-adt-组成成分\"></a> 4. 树的 ADT 组成成分</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>树的子类主要包含节点 <code>Node</code>，其构成为：</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">成员名称</th>\n<th>成员类型</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">元素</td>\n<td><code>Element e</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">父节点</td>\n<td><code>Node parent</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">子节点</td>\n<td><code>Node[] children</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>树的 ADT 成员主要包含：</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">成员名称</th>\n<th>成员类型</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">根节点</td>\n<td><code>Node root</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">树的大小</td>\n<td><code>int size</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>树的操作：</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">类型</th>\n<th>函数</th>\n<th>介绍</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">根节点</td>\n<td><code>root(): Node</code></td>\n<td>返回当前树的根节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">父节点</td>\n<td><code>parent(Node): Node</code></td>\n<td>返回该树种某个节点的父节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">子节点</td>\n<td><code>children(Node): Node[]</code></td>\n<td>返回节点的子节点或者迭代器</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">查询</td>\n<td><code>isInternal(Node): boolean</code></td>\n<td>返回节点是否是内节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">查询</td>\n<td><code>isExternal(Node): boolean</code></td>\n<td>返回节点是否是叶节点</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">树状态</td>\n<td><code>size(): int</code></td>\n<td>返回树的节点个数</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">树状态</td>\n<td><code>isEmpty(): boolean</code></td>\n<td>返回树是否为空</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"5-树的遍历traversal方法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#5-树的遍历traversal方法\"></a> 5. 树的遍历(Traversal)方法</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">遍历类型</th>\n<th>介绍</th>\n<th>伪代码</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">前序遍历<br>Preorder</td>\n<td>先访问父节点，再从左到右遍历其子节点。</td>\n<td>1. <code>Algorithm preOrder(v)</code><br>2. <code>···visit(v)</code><br>3. <code>···for each child w of v</code><br>4. <code>······preorder(w)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">后序遍历<br>Postorder</td>\n<td>先遍历子节点，再访问父节点</td>\n<td>1. <code>Algorithm postOrder(v)</code><br>2. <code>···for each child w of v</code><br>3. <code>······postorder(w)</code><br>4. <code>···visit(v)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">中序遍历<br>Inorder</td>\n<td>属于二叉树的专属。<br>先遍历左节点，再访问父节点，再遍历右节点</td>\n<td>1. <code>Algorithm inOrder(v)</code><br>2. <code>···inOrder(v.left)</code><br>3. <code>···visit(v)</code><br>4. <code>···inOrder(v.right)</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h1 id=\"二-二叉树\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#二-二叉树\"></a> 二. 二叉树</h1>\n<p>二叉树是一种抽象数据结构(ADT)。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>一般定义：</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>a tree whose each internal node has at most two children, and the children of a node are an ordered pair, though one might be “missing”.<br />\n一棵每个内部节点最多有两个子节点，并且节点的子节点是有序对的树。</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>递归定义：</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>A tree consisting of a single node, or a tree whose root has an ordered pair of “children”, each of which is missing (a null) or is the root of a binary tree.<br />\n由单个节点组成的树，或者其根具有一对有序“子节点”的树，每个子节点都缺失（为空）或为二叉树子树的根。</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>特点：</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>每个节点最多有两个子节点</li>\n<li>子节点之间是有序的，即左子节点和右子节点，可以为空节点。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"1-二叉树的大致种类\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-二叉树的大致种类\"></a> 1. 二叉树的大致种类</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>种类</th>\n<th>介绍</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>完满二叉树<br>Full Binary Tree</td>\n<td>如果二叉树的所有内部节点都具有两个子节点，那么称这个二叉树是完满二叉树。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>完美二叉树<br>Perfect Binary Tree</td>\n<td>如果一个满二叉树中所有的子节点都在同一个深度，那么称这个二叉树是完美二叉树。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>完全二叉树<br>Complete Binary Tree</td>\n<td>除了叶节点所处的深度以外，其他深度是一个完美二叉树，并且叶节点是靠右排序的二叉树是完全二叉树。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"2-二叉树的效率分析\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-二叉树的效率分析\"></a> 2. 二叉树的效率分析</h2>\n<p>求树的高度：如果树的大小为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span>，那么：<br />\n对于完美二叉树来说，时间复杂度是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Θ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Θ(log(n))</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Θ</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">o</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">g</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>。<br />\n对于非完美二叉树来说，考虑到一条链，时间复杂度是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Ω</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">Ω(log(n))</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Ω</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">o</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">g</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-二叉树的简单-cdt\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#3-二叉树的简单-cdt\"></a> 3. 二叉树的简单 CDT</h2>\n<h3 id=\"i-基于数组的二叉树-array-based-representation-of-binary-tree\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#i-基于数组的二叉树-array-based-representation-of-binary-tree\"></a> i. 基于数组的二叉树 (Array-Based Representation of Binary Tree)</h3>\n<p>它也可以被称为 树形数组(tree-as-array)。它是一种使用数组作为CDT实现二叉树ADT的方式。</p>\n<p>一般使用 <code>rank(Node): int</code> 来表示节点的数组索引。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>具有以下性质：</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">性质</th>\n<th>解释</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>rank(root) = 1</code></td>\n<td>根节点的索引是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>rank(parent(node)) = rank(node) &gt;&gt; 1</code></td>\n<td>每个节点的父节点是该节点的索引整除以 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>rank(left_child(node)) = rank(node) &lt;&lt; 1</code></td>\n<td>每个节点的左节点是该节点的索引 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\times 2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">×</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>rank(right_child(node)) = rank(node) &lt;&lt; 1 + 1</code></td>\n<td>每个节点的右节点是该节点的索引 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\times 2 + 1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">×</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>优点：</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>优点</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>能够节省空间。因为不用储存相关的指针，而是使用计算代替</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>储存能够更紧凑，具有更好的内存局部性&quot;better memory locality&quot;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>很好地解决缓存和内存层次结构的问题——当访问数组元素时，其他条目可以被拉入缓存，因此访问速度更快</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"ii-平衡二叉树\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#ii-平衡二叉树\"></a> ii. 平衡二叉树</h3>\n<p>具体请看这一篇笔记：<a href=\"%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%2F%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%2F%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%2F%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%A0%91\">二叉搜索树</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"三-树结构的导航\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#三-树结构的导航\"></a> 三. 树结构的导航</h1>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>笔记</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">树类型</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody